{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was, again, not a very long ride, because Westerbork is very much in the east of Holland-- northeast or Holland-- quite close to the German border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Belsen isn't that all that far into Germany on that side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I can't remember how long the journey took.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't even remember whether we arrived by day or night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we arrived at this railway siding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but we could see straight away that it wasn't really as gentle as Westerbork-- it all looked a lot harsher, even at the railway siding because there were SS there with dogs, and machine guns, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we all had to line up, and we were walked to the camp-- which was a couple of miles, maybe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were pretty fit in-- in those days, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We hadn't starved in any way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and we had no disease amongst us, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it wasn't really difficult to-- to do the walk to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and when we saw the camp-- well, like Westerbork, it had watchtowers and barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Westerbork actually add a moat, but there was not moat in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there was more barbed wire, and probably more strict security than we were used to at Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say so, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think women and children might have gone on the truck, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was then-- '44, '36, seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would have thought so, but I'm not sure, not sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no registration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were herded into a-- a section of the camp in Belsen-- Belsen was a very large camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Westerbork was also a very large camp, but Belsen was divided up into all sorts of different sections.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
